    "description": {
      "content": [
        {
          "content": [
            {
              "text": "*",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "marks": [
                {
                  "type": "strong"
                }
              ],
              "text": "ISSUE DESCRIPTION AND HOW TO REPRODUCE",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "*",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "content": [
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "   Multiple customers are reporting that as of earlier today, their external authentication no longer works; they either get an error or are simply not redirected to the External IdP page to finish the authentication flow as expected.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ],
              "type": "listItem"
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "  Regardless of the specific behavior each customer is facing, there's a constant; we see the exact same error in Grafana for every single customer:",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ],
              "type": "listItem"
            }
          ],
          "type": "bulletList"
        },
        {
          "content": [
            {
              "text": "GET /api/user-information/v1/profiles/me - 502 Fetch GET Error - 502 ",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "content": [
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "  [Attachment - image.png](",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "marks": [
                        {
                          "attrs": {
                            "href": "https://supportoutsystems.zendesk.com/attachments/token/iaTuczMZgfEhXzvhyWFnv6OMV/?name=image.png"
                          },
                          "type": "link"
                        }
                      ],
                      "text": "https://supportoutsystems.zendesk.com/attachments/token/iaTuczMZgfEhXzvhyWFnv6OMV/?name=image.png",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": ")",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ],
              "type": "listItem"
            }
          ],
          "type": "bulletList"
        },
        {
          "content": [
            {
              "text": "*",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "marks": [
                {
                  "type": "strong"
                }
              ],
              "text": "IMPACT ON THE CUSTOMER",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "*",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "content": [
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "   This is completely preventing external authentication from working, and multiple customers have reported this to us in the past few hours. We'll share a complete list of those who've reported this to us in a comment shortly after this escalation is created.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ],
              "type": "listItem"
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "   We can also this is impacting multiple customers in Grafana (",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "marks": [
                        {
                          "attrs": {
                            "href": "https://outsystems.grafana.net/goto/df1mi4oviyosgc?orgId=1):"
                          },
                          "type": "link"
                        }
                      ],
                      "text": "https://outsystems.grafana.net/goto/df1mi4oviyosgc?orgId=1):",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "(",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "marks": [
                        {
                          "attrs": {
                            "href": "https://outsystems.grafana.net/goto/df1mi4oviyosgc?orgId=1):"
                          },
                          "type": "link"
                        }
                      ],
                      "text": "https://outsystems.grafana.net/goto/df1mi4oviyosgc?orgId=1\\):",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": ")",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ],
              "type": "listItem"
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "  [Attachment - image.png](",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "marks": [
                        {
                          "attrs": {
                            "href": "https://supportoutsystems.zendesk.com/attachments/token/tHH0TgQVQyBCJoxJcdudAmKBu/?name=image.png"
                          },
                          "type": "link"
                        }
                      ],
                      "text": "https://supportoutsystems.zendesk.com/attachments/token/tHH0TgQVQyBCJoxJcdudAmKBu/?name=image.png",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": ")",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ],
              "type": "listItem"
            }
          ],
          "type": "bulletList"
        },
        {
          "content": [
            {
              "text": "*",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "marks": [
                {
                  "type": "strong"
                }
              ],
              "text": "TROUBLESHOOTING STEPS \u0026 WORKAROUND",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "*",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "content": [
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "   We've suggested that a customer unassign and reassign the IdP to their Production Stage as an attempt to mitigate this, but the customer still hasn't gotten back to us to let us know if it worked, and beyond that, this error is completely unprecedented for us.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ],
              "type": "listItem"
            }
          ],
          "type": "bulletList"
        },
